paragraphs.text:
%md
# This simple Oracle Machine Learning Studio notebook will get you started with the basics!

###
1. Data Selection
2. Data Viewing
3. Graphs
4. Data Analysis

### Fun, simple, easy!  We're going to look at the CARS dataset 

####  CARS Description
* MPG, miles per gallon
* Cylinders(4, 6, 8, etc. including rotary engines)
* Horsepower
* Weight
* Acceleration (smaller is faster!)
* Year(1970 - 1990)
* Origin (1,3,'USA','Japan','Europe')

##### * See http://davis.wpi.edu/xmdv/datasets/cars.html for more information)
